# portability-denylist — OPTIONAL extra tokens for portability-lint.sh
#
# Copy this file to `tools/portability-denylist.txt` if you fork/dogfood the plugin inside your
# own org and want the lint to also fail when YOUR project-specific tokens leak into the generic
# plugin tree. One extended-regex (ERE) per line. Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
# The public plugin ships WITHOUT an active denylist, so it stays org-neutral.
#
# Examples (uncomment / edit for your org):
# acme-corp
# AcmeCorp
# PROJ-[0-9]+
# acme\.atlassian\.net
# \bDjango\b
# apps/(web|mobile|backend)
